Renaissance Capital Appoints Ali Khalpey as Equities Head in South Africa

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-06-08T10:15:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/renaissance-capital-appoints-ali-khalpey-as-equities-head-in-south-africa.html
Renaissance Capital  said it appointed
Ali Khalpey as head of equities in  South Africa .  Khalpey joined Renaissance in January last year and will
retain his responsibility as head of sales for  Africa ,
Renaissance said in an e-mailed statement from Moscow today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  